  "body": "**Kubernetes version** (use `kubectl version`): 1.4.0\n\n**Environment**:\n- **Cloud provider or hardware configuration**: Azure\n\n**What happened**:\nTrying to mount an Azure file share by following the directions [here](https://github.com/kubernetes/kubernetes/tree/master/examples/volumes/azure_file) fails because hyperkube does not include cifs-utils (eg, `mount.cifs`).\n\nCan this be added to the hyperkube image, please?\n",
